Holly Willoughby, 41, treated her fans to a makeup free snap of herself posing in a white bikini as she enjoyed the sunshine in a very picturesque location. The This Morning presenter looked glowing as she smiled fresh-faced.Her blonde hair was wet after taking a dip in the clear water next to a rocky backdrop.The stunning snap was shared to the Instagram of Holly’s lifestyle brand, Wylde Moon.The caption read: “Swimwear season is upon us, and although this can be an extremely daunting time for many (us included), fear not.“Our resident WYLDE Style guru @danniiwhiteman is here to guide you through swimwear to suit all shapes, sizes, and budgets!”